  "name": "Morrison COU1 — CPB hemolysis credibility assessment (W-EP-04 adversarial)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under cardiopulmonary bypass (CPB) conditions. COU1 evaluates whether the computational model can identify worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for a Class II CPB device at Model Risk Level 3. Twelve of thirteen factors are assessed; the 'Use error' factor is marked not-assessed on the rationale that operator interaction is absent from automated CFD workflows — an argument that conflates not-applicable with not-assessed and leaves a material credibility gap at MRL 3.",
